(example const hexNumbers = ['1', '2'........, '9', 'A','B'......'F']; )
4.THEN WE TARGET BUTTON FROM HTML, BODY AND HEX SPAN
5.THEN WE ADD CLICK ADD EVENT LISTENER WITH CALLBACK FUNCTION
6.CREATE FUNCTION 
( create variable let hexColor = '#'; 
we create for loop, then we inside loop want randomly numbers
let random = Math.floor(Math.random() * array of numbers.length,
and we add it to hexColor # += hexnumbers[random] ) 
7.STYLE BACKGROUND COLOR 
(body.style.backgroundColor = hexCol;
hex.innerHTML = hexCol;)
